        "content": "## 1. Trigger & Incident Input\n\nManual Trigger for testing. Swap in a **Webhook Trigger** later without changing downstream logic — just keep the same field names (incident_id, incident_description, location, reporter_name, contact_number, date_time) that \"Set Incident Data\" produces.",
