    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 2. AI Incident Analyzer\n\nGoogle Gemini + AI Agent. Classifies disaster_type, severity, priority, people_at_risk, recommended teams/vehicles, response time and a summary. Structured Output Parser returns clean JSON under `$json.output`.",
