      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 6. Notify & Log\n\nGmail sends the alert email; Google Sheets appends a full incident record. Both use placeholder credentials.\n\n### Error Handling\nEvery API/AI node uses **Continue On Error** so a single failed call does not stop the whole response pipeline.\n\n### Extensible\nWebhook, Maps, Telegram, Slack, SMS, PDF reports and dashboards can be added by branching off the existing nodes.",
        "height": 200,
        "width": 300
